		<title>(VIDEO) Robotic-assisted bronchoscopy study of more than 2,000 lung lesions suggests safer, faster path to diagnosing lung cancer</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/video-robotic-assisted-bronchoscopy-study-of-more-than-2000-lung-lesions-suggests-safer-faster-path-to-diagnosing-lung-cancer/
		
		<dc:creator><!--[CDATA[Alison Satake]]--></dc:creator>
		<pubdate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 13:00:00 +0000</pubdate>
				<category><!--[CDATA[Cancer]]--></category>
