<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-minute-advancing-colorectal-cancer-care-through-innovation-and-screening/">Mayo Clinic Minute: Advancing colorectal cancer care through innovation and screening</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
